<br />
Arnold Skolnick, ed., Paintings of the Southwest (New York: Clarkson, Potter Publishers, 1994, p. 13 ill.<br />
<br />
Patricia Trenton, Sandra D’Emilio, Independent Spirits: Women Painters of the American West, 1890-1945 (Autry Museum of Western Heritage/University of California Press, 1995).<br />
<br />
